paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted genetic variant information for the KCNH2 gene, including penetrance data.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: Case 5 exhibited seizures before becoming unresponsive carried two variants, R1047L in KCNH2 and R1193Q in SCN5A.

functional_data.summary: R1047L was initially described as a polymorphism but is present more often in subjects with Torsades-de-Pointes than in controls during metabolic stress.

variants.segregation_data: The family could not be contacted.
variants.additional_notes: R1047L is present more often in subjects with Torsades-de-Pointes than in controls during metabolic stress.
